## [1.0.0] - 2021-09-08
### Added
- Gateway Service.														--Gabriel  & Estella--			
- Login Controller for log in functionality.							--Edward--
- User authentication and authorization.								--Edward--
- Password encription through BCrypt encoding.							--Edward--
- Form validation for login screen (user credentials).					--Edward--			
- Test user role for development and testing purposes.					--Edward--


- User database (PostreSQL).											--Edward--
- SpringBoot connection to User database.								--Gabriel--
- User Model with properties (id, username, password).					--Edward--

- User Service.															--Gabriel & Estella--
- User Controller for user database queries.							--Edward--
- Function to fetch users from database by provided username.			--Edward--
- Migration support through Flyway.										--Edward--

- P4Admin web-interface.												--Alex--
- Auto confirguration for PostgreSQL database provisioning for P4Admin.	--Alex--

- Client Service.														--Gabriel & Estella--
- Login page.															--Gabriel--
- Tagging page.															--Gabriel--
- Integration for adnotation component for Konva.js (static integration).--Gabriel--
- Functionalities for tagging window :"select", "create-point",			--Gabriel--
 "create-box", "create-polygon", "create-line", "create-expanding-line",
 "show-mask" (static).

- Tagging Service.														--Gabriel & Estella--

- Query Service.														--Gabriel & Estella--
- COCO Datatype Controller for COCO database queries.					--Alex--
- COCO dataype manipulation features.									--Alex--

- COCO database (MongoDB).												--Estella--
- Importing of COCO datatypes and Model classes with coresponding properties.		--Estella--

### Changed
- Started using password encryption with BcryptEncoding encoding.		--Edward--
- Started using Zuul routing in Gateway instead of Spring routing for MVC support.	--Edward--